{
  "stem": "1684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 513.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they came in, identification.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I showed them the marriage paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I thought that that's fine, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This will keep me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he said, you come with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, this was a big building too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And everybody who was taken down there in the building, it was screaming all terrible.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Everybody was shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And going down the steps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I showed him-- when I showed him the marriage licence, he said, that's nice, and you come with me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my husband said to me, why don't you show him the Juden pass with his picture and with his age on it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I said, here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This-- this is my Juden pass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So he shut up, and he said, you can stay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was saved for that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But of course, it wasn't the end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Right after that, there was another deportation, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You and your husband were still friends at this point?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were still friends at this point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, not only were we friends-- in 1942, after everything, my husband said, we have to get married.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- we were afraid to get married because the gestapo wouldn't allow us to get married.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But was-- we were-- I was like standing in the kitchen, and my husband said, you know, somebody die, and a rabbi's coming in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were like, about eight of nine people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But outside, there were some people who did not show up for work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were 17 people shot in front of our house at the day we were married.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it wasn't [INAUDIBLE] I mean, it wasn't a ceremony.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was just, a rabbi gave us, like, [INAUDIBLE], which means he-- he married us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My husband had a little ring made for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
